      "text": "この人はね……\nアイドルが好きなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me tell you about this guy‚\nhe loves idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.750113614400227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_16_05-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "みんなを楽しませることが出来る、凄い力を持った\nアイドルを見たい、育てたいって……誰よりも思ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To him‚ idols are incredibly powerful people who bring joy to everyone.\nHe wants to watch idols. He wants to help them grow… more than anyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.0167802810669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
